{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01KPzvcZPnAnnGHK3d1zCbaZ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01EN5B3fSHY5UFBGpr1HuQsz","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /mydata/karma/runs/short-rerun/elasticsearch-full-lifecycle-20260618_105654/stages/stage_05\ncat > submit.txt <<'EOF'\nAdded two new Elasticsearch data nodes and relocated app-data shards onto them.\n\nWhat I did:\n1. Created a SEPARATE StatefulSet `es-data-new` (replicas=2) joining the existing\n   `es-cluster` cluster, with its own headless Service `es-data-new` and a ConfigMap\n   `es-config-new`. The new nodes reuse the cluster's TLS (es-http-tls) and file-realm\n   (es-file-realm-aggregate) secrets, set discovery.seed_hosts to es-cluster-0/1/2,\n   run as node.roles [data, ingest] (non-master, so master quorum is unchanged), and\n   carry the allocation attribute `node.attr.zone: new`. The original 3 nodes have no\n   zone attribute, so the new nodeset is distinguished.\n2. Set `index.routing.allocation.require.zone=new` on app-data; its shards relocated\n   onto es-data-new-0/1.\n3. The original es-cluster pods were stuck NotReady because their baked\n   ELASTIC_PASSWORD env was stale versus the current `elastic-password` secret\n   (readiness probe got 401). Ran `kubectl rollout restart statefulset/es-cluster`\n   (replicas unchanged at 3) so they re-read the current secret and became Ready,\n   restoring the es-http service endpoints. No operators/CRDs installed.\n\nVerification (via es-http through curl-test):\n1. Cluster health: green, number_of_nodes=5.\n2. app-data shards (shard 0 p + r) STARTED on es-data-new-1 / es-data-new-0 — outside\n   the original 3.\n3. New nodes carry node.attr zone=new; original nodes have no zone attribute.\n4. es-cluster StatefulSet still at 3 replicas.\nEOF\necho \"written\"; cat submit.txt | head -3","description":"Write submit.txt"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":305,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1145,"cache_read_input_tokens":65317,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1145},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"666944db-1f25-46b3-a9c4-6c32d64fae85","uuid":"91402215-e246-49a8-a3ca-9ca8e3ed5c07","request_id":"req_011CcAgt3tay5nfaqiHucLRh"}
